Resource Profile: openIMIS CoverageEligibilityRequest

Official URL: https://github.com/openimis/openimis_fhir_r5_ig/StructureDefinition/openimis-coverage-eligibility-request Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-26 Computable Name: OpenIMISCoverageEligibilityRequest

Defines a CoverageEligibilityRequest for openIMIS to enquire an Insuree.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: openIMIS CoverageEligibilityResponse
  • Examples for this Profile: CoverageEligibilityRequest/JoeDoeEnquiring
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: openIMIS Capability Statement
